19
00:03:23,328 --> 00:03:24,537
My goodness!

20
00:03:25,288 --> 00:03:28,124
-Ki-baek is famous, isn't he?
-Don't be surprised.

21
00:03:29,375 --> 00:03:30,501
LET US LOVE EACH OTHER

22
00:03:30,585 --> 00:03:31,794
"On Woo-ju"?

23
00:03:33,338 --> 00:03:34,172
Ms. On's daughter?

24
00:03:35,632 --> 00:03:37,842
WE'RE CLOSED TODAY
MADAME ON

25
